Enum Class FacilityTypeDefinition

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<FacilityTypeDefinition>, Constable
public enum FacilityTypeDefinition extends Enum<FacilityTypeDefinition>
The FacilityTypeDefinition is used to feed the definition of the FacilityTypes valid value set for Coco Pharmaceuticals' sustainability program.
